## Clean


::: {.cell}

```{.r .cell-code}
snyder_clean <- snyder |> mutate(
  datetime_arrest = mdy_hm(datetime_arrest),
  date_arrest = date(datetime_arrest)
) |> select(
  -officer,
  -charge_desc,
  -city_zip
) |> cbind(age = NA, race = NA, sex = NA, ethnicity = NA, agency_arrest = NA)

snyder_clean |> glimpse()
```
